name: .CRYPTED File Extension
summary: Learn about .CRYPTED files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: A CRYPTED file is an encrypted file created by WinOptimizer, a maintenance and optimization program for Windows. It contains the encrypted version of an individual file. CRYPTED files can be decrypted with WinOptimizer using the password used to encrypt the file.
